"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*注：主持人Metatime ，回答者，metatime社区大使Dark Moon，简单起见用首字母表示问答*\\n\\n\\\\--Hello everyone, AMA starts now. Metatime's community ambassador Darkmoon is here with us to answer the questions.\\n\\n中文翻译：大家好，AMA现在开始。 Metatime 的社区大使 Darkmoon 在这里与我们一起回答问题。\\n\\n3\\\\.\\n\\n**M:** What is the dual-token model of Metatime? What are the use cases of TIME and MATTER?\\n\\nMetatime的双通证模型是什么？ TIME 和 MATTER 的用例是什么？\\n\\nD: MATTER is collected from Metatime’s task system. Currently, the main tasks include the immersion time on Metatime, your content gaining reading time from others, and reporting inappropriate content, etc. In such cases, MATTER serves as an incentive token.\\n\\nMATTER 是从 Metatime 的任务系统中收集的。目前主要的任务包括在Metatime上的沉浸时间，你的内容从他人那里获得阅读时间，以及举报不当内容等。在这种情况下，MATTER作为激励令牌。\\n\\nThe value of Matter will come from Metatime’s upcoming feature updates: Tribe, Reputation NFT system, content-as-asset feature, mirroring city, etc.\\n\\nMatter 的价值将来自 Metatime 即将推出的功能更新：部落、声誉 NFT 系统、内容即资产功能、镜像城市等。\\n\\n4\\\\.\\n\\n**M:** I'd like to know what is the roadmap for 2022 Q1?\\n\\n我想知道 2022 年第一季度的路线图是什么？\\n\\n**D:**You may also check our full roadmap on our website: <https://metatime.social/>\\n\\n您也可以在我们的网站上查看我们的完整路线图\\n\\nIn 22Q1, We will unlock many new features, including tribe/reputation NFT system.\\n\\nwe also will make the transition to decentralization, and the right of censoring content will be returned to the community.\\n\\nNew user introduction program will also be implemented in Q1.\\n\\n在 22Q1，我们将解锁许多新功能，包括部落/声誉 NFT 系统。 我们也将向去中心化过渡，审查内容的权利将归还给社区。 新用户介绍计划也将在第一季度实施。\\n\\n5\\\\.\\n\\n**M**: Please give an overview of the feature \\\"Tribe\\\".\\n\\n请概述“部落”功能。\\n\\n**D**: Tribe is a new species of social product, a forum-based, blockchain-transformed web 3 application.\\n\\nTribe 是一种新的社交产品，一种基于论坛、区块链改造的 Web 3 应用程序。\\n\\nAlso, the ownership of the tribe is an NFT, and the ownership can be transferred.\\n\\nThis means that the tribe itself can be priced out of the secondary market, and the owner of an active tribe with quality content can transfer ownership of the tribe ...\\n\\n另外，部落的所有权是NFT，所有权可以转让。 这意味着部落本身可以被定价出二级市场，拥有优质内容的活跃部落的拥有者可以转让部落的所有权……\\n\\nin addition to being rewarded with TIME. Thus will greatly increasing their motivation to create and maintain an active tribe.\\n\\n除了获得 TIME 奖励。因此将大大增加他们创建和维护一个活跃部落的动力。\\n\\nSimply put, Any user can create a \\\"tribe\\\" for any topic after consuming matter. Tribes can be set up as paid or free, as determined by the tribe owner. The tribe owner gets the revenue from the content of the tribe, so he will work hard to promote and manage the tribe\\n\\n简单的说，任何用户消费物质后，都可以为任何话题创建一个“部落”。部落可以设置为付费或免费，由部落所有者决定。部落主从部落的内容中获得收益，因此他会努力推动和管理部落。\\n\\n6\\\\.\\n\\nM: We found out the teamannounced many partners. How will they generate the content in Metatime, and what are the incentivesfor them?\\n\\n**M:**我们发现团队宣布了许多合作伙伴。他们将如何在 Metatime 中生成内容，对他们的激励是什么？\\n\\nD: In addition, under the mechanism of metatime, the platform will gradually deposit a group of crypto-native users with expertise with which they can have close contact, thus benefiting the development of their projects.\\n\\n**D:**此外，在元时间机制下，平台将逐步沉淀一批具有专业知识的加密原生用户，可以与之密切接触，从而有利于他们项目的发展。\\n\\nOur partners are required to have NFT to log in to Metatime, just like regular users.\\n\\nThe benefits they can get come from multiple sources: First obviously is the [$TIME ](https://app.metatime.social/)incentive that their content gets; Secondly, Metatime is a social product that can meet their market needs.\\n\\n我们的合作伙伴需要有 NFT 才能登录 Metatime，就像普通用户一样。 他们可以获得的好处来自多个来源：首先显然是他们的内容获得的 $TIME 激励；其次，Metatime是一款能够满足其市场需求的社交产品。\\n\\n7\\\\.\\n\\n**M**：  What's the plan about the added value for the first 2000 Avatars? Could the team help share in advance?\\n\\n关于前2000个头像的附加值有什么计划？团队能否提前帮助分享一下？\\n\\n**D**:    We certainly have planned well, but I can't reveal too much right now, stay tuned👀\\n\\n我们当然有很好的计划，但我现在不能透露太多，请继续关注👀\\n\\n8\\\\.\\n\\n**M**:Will the Entry threshold always be so high, because now 10000AF cost $270 ?How do we achieve the network effect?Will the community threshold be gradually lowered in the later period?\\n\\n进入门槛会一直这么高吗，因为现在10000AF的价格是270美元，我们如何实现网络效应？\\\"社区门槛 \\\"会在后期逐渐降低吗？\\n\\n**D**:  \\\"Will the Entry threshold always be so high?\\\"\\n\\nOf course not, we are a social product and the network effect is exactly what we need.\\n\\nBut we already have plans to open up the next batch of users to the Metatime product, and we'll probably announce it in January, stay tuned!\\n\\nThe current limitations are mainly due to the fact that we are still in beta testing phase, where there are still many necessary features being refined, and features such as tribe, reputation NFT being developed.\\n\\n当然不会，我们是一个社交产品，网络效应正是我们需要的。\\n\\n但是我们已经有计划开放下一批用户进入Metatime产品，我们可能会在一月份宣布，敬请关注！\\\"。\\n\\n目前的限制主要是由于我们还处于测试阶段，还有很多必要的功能正在完善，诸如部落、声誉NFT等功能正在开发。\\n\\n9\\\\.\\n\\n**M**:  How to solve the problem of content supply at the beginning of the community?Make sure the creators are serious about sharing quality content and not getting rewarded with pornographic images, following each other, and other lazy ways.\\n\\n如何解决社区初期的内容供应问题？确保创作者认真分享高质量的内容，而不是通过色情图片、互相关注等偷懒的方式获得回报。\\n\\n**D**:We certainly took this into account, and if you look closely you'll see that metatime initially had far less pornographic spam than a competing product that had gone live before.\\n\\nIn addition to this, the [$MATTER ](https://app.metatime.social/)incentive for posting quality content and the fact that we have set aside a reporting task within the task system will also help us achieve this.\\n\\nThe need to consume [$time ](https://app.metatime.social/)in order to use metatime, which is the most essential reason why we can keep our content clean in the long run.\\n\\n我们当然考虑到了这一点，如果你仔细观察就会发现，metatime最初的色情垃圾信息远远少于之前上线的竞争产品。\\n\\n除此之外，$MATTER对发布高质量内容的激励，以及我们在任务系统中预留了一个报告任务，也会帮助我们实现这个目标。\\n\\n需要消耗$时间才能使用元时间，这也是我们能长期保持内容清洁的最基本原因。\\n\\n**M**:Due to time limitations, this AMA will end here. If you have any other questions, you can still leave comments or discuss them in the Telegram group, where our volunteers will also answer them.\\n\\n由于时间限制，本次AMA将在此结束。如果你有任何其他问题，你仍然可以在Telegram组中留言或讨论，我们的志愿者也会在那里回答。\\n\\nMetatime[链接](https://app.metatime.social/)   \\n \",\"timestamp\":1640871539,\"title\":\"metatime AMA内容整理\"},\"digest\":\"ytliAQ0vaBv1nK3BX8W_smifqV82VN09QSXyF43eC3Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x88F598a446Dd3696F02DdCc98b95dd7d45Dc1719\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qfDWoYDMhl-yiLaKC4Uq2mdz-YYDCo3UsocsN1GDY8Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JxRO0tK3PduC0NU5pxe1JvUXOPYqwNI_APYJTkg2a4E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"UlGe-jNav62eOm9xbRsMr5jBmhmkOeFBbj0tqFoHMeEkfYOoGt78-g5Tx8PWydvTTK4LNeeme4W1-4AblSw0iQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9873a8fb69cc46f693ef61d078b6a8cd883f78c668248f633c7bf743a10fa6622297ea3b92ba9082880e591e6123f5123c6f245b409d1308e6aa5b991307f9c71b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qfDWoYDMhl-yiLaKC4Uq2mdz-YYDCo3UsocsN1GDY8Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JxRO0tK3PduC0NU5pxe1JvUXOPYqwNI_APYJTkg2a4E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ytliAQ0vaBv1nK3BX8W_smifqV82VN09QSXyF43eC3Y\"}"